      "date": "2013-09-18 11:51:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6fb35e72-2052-11e3-b50d-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
